  <description><![CDATA[<p>Facing the slopes, Hotel Ladinia occupies an excellent position for both the centre and ski lifts. Set just a stone’s throw from the Doninz lift, this attractively furnished property is known for its traditional ambiance. The hotel’s café is arguably the social hub of La Villa with guests and locals alike passing time and enjoying the view. The wellness area has been newly renovated and is on hand to soothe any aching muscles after a great day on the mountain.</p>]]></description>
